    "id": "overview"
  }, "OVERVIEW"), mdx("p", null, "The Webizen Platform is intended to be a force for good, as is an overriding objective of significance.\xA0 The platform itself; is intended to support an information management system that works in a way that is different to other known \u2018operating systems\u2019, application environments and consequently thereafter - information management solutions.\xA0 These works are complex, and consider various \u2018spheres\u2019 from the technical (infosphere) to the socio-sphere, economic, legal, biosphere, etc. The platform has a focus on producing ecosystem solutions to usefully employ AI."), mdx("h3", {
